<p>1</p>
<p>（1）<code v-pre>Normalized Throttle</code>为归一化后的油门，归一化的同时，考虑了压降，其定义为</p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-error" title="ParseError: KaTeX parse error: Expected &#x27;EOF&#x27;, got &#x27;_&#x27; at position 119: …WM}_{\text{spin_̲min}}}{\text{PW…" style="color:#cc0000">
\begin{aligned}
\text{throttle}_{\text{norm}}&amp;=\frac{V}{V_{\text{max}}}max(0, \frac{\text{PWM}-\text{PWM}_{\text{spin_min}}}{\text{PWM}_{\text{spin_max}}-\text{PWM}_{\text{spin_min}}})\\
&amp;=\frac{21.68}{21.72}max(0, \frac{1555-1150}{1950-1150})\\
&amp;=0.9982\times 0.5063\\
&amp;=0.5053
\end{aligned}
</span></p>
<p>（2）<code v-pre>Normalized Thrust</code>为由归一化后的油门计算得到的推力，其定义为</p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mtable rowspacing="0.25em" columnalign="right left" columnspacing="0em"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><msub><mtext>thrust</mtext><mtext>norm</mtext></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mtext>EXPO</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>⋅</mo><msub><mtext>throttle</mtext><mtext>norm</mtext></msub><mo>+</mo><mtext>EXPO</mtext><mo>⋅</mo><msubsup><mtext>throttle</mtext><mtext>norm</mtext><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo separator="true">,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>×</mo><mn>0.5053</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.505</mn><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0.25265</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>0.12766</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0.3803</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\begin{aligned}
\text{thrust}_{\text{norm}}&amp;=max((1-\text{EXPO})\cdot \text{throttle}_{\text{norm}} + \text{EXPO}\cdot \text{throttle}_{\text{norm}}^2,0)\\
&amp;=(1-0.5)\times 0.5053 + 0.5\times 0.5053^2\\
&amp;=0.25265+0.12766\\
&amp;=0.3803
\end{aligned}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:6.0826em;vertical-align:-2.7913em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mtable"><span class="col-align-r"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:3.2913em;"><span style="top:-5.3928em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">thrust</span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord text mtight"><span class="mord mtight">norm</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.8687em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"></span></span><span style="top:-2.3687em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"></span></span><span style="top:-0.8687em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:2.7913em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="col-align-l"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:3.2913em;"><span style="top:-5.3928em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">ma</span><span class